    "I didn't show up because I prefer to be fashionably absent.": "No aparecí porque prefiero estar ausente con estilo.",
    "My alarm clock and I had a fight, and it won by not ringing.": "Mi despertador y yo tuvimos una pelea, y ganó al no sonar.",
